statements: SELECT material_name, density FROM biomechanical_properties_materials;
SELECT * FROM biomechanical_properties_materials WHERE elastic_modulus > 1000;
SELECT material_name, yield_strength FROM biomechanical_properties_materials ORDER BY yield_strength DESC;
SELECT material_name, density FROM biomechanical_properties_materials WHERE ultimate_tensile_strength < 500;
SELECT material_name, elastic_modulus, ultimate_tensile_strength FROM biomechanical_properties_materials WHERE density BETWEEN 2.0 AND 3.0;
SELECT * FROM biomechanical_properties_materials WHERE density > 1.5 ORDER BY material_name ASC LIMIT 10
SELECT material_id, material_name, elastic_modulus FROM biomechanical_properties_materials WHERE ultimate_tensile_strength > 300 ORDER BY elastic_modulus DESC LIMIT 5

SELECT material_id, material_name, density, elastic_modulus, yield_strength FROM biomechanical_properties_materials WHERE density < 2.0 AND yield_strength > 200 ORDER BY density DESC, elastic_modulus ASC LIMIT 8
SELECT material_name, ultimate_tensile_strength FROM biomechanical_properties_materials WHERE ultimate_tensile_strength BETWEEN 250 AND 400 ORDER BY ultimate_tensile_strength LIMIT 6
SELECT material_name, density, yield_strength FROM biomechanical_properties_materials WHERE yield_strength < 150 OR density < 1.0 ORDER BY density ASC LIMIT 4
SELECT material_name, density FROM biomechanical_properties
SELECT material_name, elasticity FROM biomechanical_properties WHERE density > 0.5
SELECT prosthetic_type, used_for FROM prosthetics ORDER BY prosthetic_id DESC
SELECT * FROM biomechanical_properties WHERE elasticity < 500
SELECT prosthetic_type, material_name FROM prosthetics INNER JOIN biomechanical_properties ON prosthetics.material_id = biomechanical_properties.material_id
SELECT * FROM biomechanical_properties WHERE elasticity > 100 ORDER BY material_name DESC;
SELECT prosthetic_type, used_for FROM prosthetics WHERE material_id IN (1, 2, 3) AND prosthetic_type LIKE '%leg%' ORDER BY prosthetic_type ASC;
SELECT material_name, density, elasticity FROM biomechanical_properties WHERE density BETWEEN 0.7 AND 1.2 ORDER BY density, elasticity DESC;

SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_prosthetics, bp.material_name FROM prosthetics AS p LEFT JOIN biomechanical_properties AS bp ON p.material_id = bp.material_id GROUP BY bp.material_name ORDER BY total_prosthetics DESC;

SELECT p.prosthetic_type, bp.density, bp.elasticity FROM prosthetics AS p JOIN biomechanical_properties AS bp ON p.material_id = bp.material_id WHERE bp.density > 1.0 ORDER BY bp.elasticity DESC, p.prosthetic_type ASC;
SELECT * FROM biomechanical_properties_of_materials;
SELECT material_name, elasticity FROM biomechanical_properties_of_materials WHERE elasticity > 100;
SELECT prosthetic_type, material_name FROM prosthetics_info JOIN biomechanical_properties_of_materials ON prosthetics_info.material_id = biomechanical_properties_of_materials.material_id;
SELECT * FROM material_tests WHERE test_result BETWEEN 50 AND 100;
SELECT material_id, test_type, test_date FROM material_tests ORDER BY test_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM biomechanical_properties_of_materials;
SELECT material_name, elasticity FROM biomechanical_properties_of_materials WHERE strength > 50;
SELECT prosthetic_type, material_name FROM prosthetics_info JOIN biomechanical_properties_of_materials ON prosthetics_info.material_id = biomechanical_properties_of_materials.material_id;
SELECT test_type, test_result, test_date FROM material_tests WHERE material_id = 3 ORDER BY test_date DESC;
SELECT DISTINCT material_name, strength FROM biomechanical_properties_of_materials WHERE elasticity > 100 ORDER BY strength DESC;
SELECT * FROM biomechanics_materials;
SELECT material_name, density FROM biomechanics_materials ORDER BY material_name DESC;
SELECT user_name, age, gender FROM prosthetic_users WHERE age > 30;
SELECT part_name, weight FROM prosthetic_parts WHERE weight < 2.5 ORDER BY part_name ASC;
SELECT user_name, part_name, usage_date FROM prosthetic_users JOIN usage_log ON prosthetic_users.user_id = usage_log.user_id JOIN prosthetic_parts ON usage_log.part_id = prosthetic_parts.part_id;
SELECT * FROM biomechanics_materials WHERE density > 1000 ORDER BY material_name DESC;
SELECT user_name, age, gender FROM prosthetic_users WHERE age >= 30 AND gender = 'Male';
SELECT part_name, weight, material_name FROM prosthetic_parts JOIN biomechanics_materials ON prosthetic_parts.material_id = biomechanics_materials.material_id;
SELECT material_name, AVG(density) AS avg_density FROM biomechanics_materials GROUP BY material_name HAVING avg_density > 800;
SELECT user_name, COUNT(*) AS part_usage_count FROM prosthetic_users JOIN usage_log ON prosthetic_users.user_id = usage_log.user_id GROUP BY user_name ORDER BY part_usage_count DESC;
SELECT * FROM biomechanical_properties_orthopedic_implants;
SELECT material_name, density, tensile_strength FROM biomechanical_properties_prosthetic_limbs;
SELECT joint_id, stability, range_of_motion FROM biomechanical_properties_joint_implants ORDER BY stability DESC;
SELECT * FROM biomechanical_properties_material_library WHERE bending_modulus > 1000;
SELECT material_name, test_type, test_result FROM biomechanical_properties_mechanical_testing WHERE test_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM biomechanical_properties_orthopedic_implants;
SELECT material_name, density, tensile_strength FROM biomechanical_properties_prosthetic_limbs WHERE flexibility > 0.5 ORDER BY durability DESC;
SELECT joint_id, material_name, range_of_motion, wear_resistance FROM biomechanical_properties_joint_implants WHERE stability < 0.8;
SELECT * FROM biomechanical_properties_material_library WHERE density > 500 OR bending_modulus < 200;
SELECT test_id, material_name, test_type, test_result FROM biomechanical_properties_mechanical_testing ORDER BY test_date DESC, test_result ASC;
